data.title: DAKINE Brett Simpson Surfing
data.description: WOW! He took down Parko in a monumental heat and went on to beat Damien in the next round.  The Huntington Boy showed the world that he will go!  Brett was hands down one of the standouts of the event!

data.title: DAKINE Damien Hobgood Surfing
data.description: Another favorite to win the Tahiti Pro, had a shocker and lost early.  Damien and CJ were both on tap and made it look too easy.
